"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?12/1/12313?source=see_link\">",
"      Bee, yellow jacket, wasp, and other Hymenoptera stings: Reaction types and acute management",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/29/14808?source=see_link\">",
"      Clinical manifestations of food allergy: An overview",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
