"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?40/17/41241?source=see_link\">",
"      Drug eruptions",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/13/1241?source=see_link\">",
