"      Apresoline (AU, BB, BF, BJ, BM, BS, BZ, CI, ET, GB, GH, GM, GN, GY, IE, JM, KE, LR, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, NE, NG, NL, NZ, PH, SC, SD, SG, SL, SN, SR, TH, TN, TT, TW, TZ, UG, ZM, ZW);",
"     </li>",
